  "1787230": {
    "name": "Ahoy",
    "steam_appid": 1787230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/16ace23bf5d9f6b1d713adcfa8bb27b7.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/16ace23bf5d9f6b1d713adcfa8bb27b7.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/16ace23bf5d9f6b1d713adcfa8bb27b7.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>让自己沉浸在惊险刺激的《Ahoy》世界中，这是一款以 18 世纪晚期加勒比海的历史时代为背景的沉浸式海军冒险游戏。这款游戏将为玩家带来丰富的体验，玩家的决定将左右故事的发展，影响新世界的命运。准备迎接一个关于自由、勇气和大海不屈召唤的动人故事吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/618d11d3394ac1449b0ba2ab2f4d8566.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/618d11d3394ac1449b0ba2ab2f4d8566.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/618d11d3394ac1449b0ba2ab2f4d8566.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险等待着您</h2>当您的角色在加勒比海波涛汹涌的水域中航行时，他们必须适应，否则就会灭亡。名声越大，权力越大，但每种权力都有其代价。您的选择将引发殖民帝国、土著居民和大胆海盗之间的冲突。在玩家和人工智能船员的陪伴下，您将主宰加勒比海的命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/57553c3e4a0ea08aa8dfce552edd2507.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/57553c3e4a0ea08aa8dfce552edd2507.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/57553c3e4a0ea08aa8dfce552edd2507.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索与发现[/h2］加勒比海充满活力和多样性的环境提供了无数探索机会。从熙熙攘攘的贸易航线到僻静的海盗海湾，玩家在航行过程中必须掌握各种航海技术和策略。每一个决定都会影响你的旅程，在世界上留下独特的印记。用自己的方式创造传奇、结交盟友、击败敌人、迎接挑战。没有两次航行是相同的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/e4161e6ff94a580aca96473be6909363.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/e4161e6ff94a580aca96473be6909363.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/e4161e6ff94a580aca96473be6909363.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >历史真实</h2>Ahoy 的每艘船都经过精心重建，坚定不移地致力于历史的真实性。每个舱室、绳索、环和铰链都是根据真实的历史文物、蓝图和模型制作的。除了引人入胜的游戏体验外，Ahoy 还是一种教育之旅。该游戏通过对 18 世纪后期航海世界中流行的术语和技术进行详细解释和演示，丰富了玩家对海洋生物的理解。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6dee96f80e0bcc6c79bcf148d90e7450.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6dee96f80e0bcc6c79bcf148d90e7450.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6dee96f80e0bcc6c79bcf148d90e7450.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >海战</h2>Ahoy的战斗采用了真实的海军和肉搏战机制。以第一人称视角指挥你的船员，利用风，管理你的武器库，同时在充满互动元素的环境中与人工智能和玩家船长对抗。无论你是与船员一起计划完美的战略，还是用意想不到的动作震惊你的盟友，驾驭关系都与在海上航行一样重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6ba5f74cd04874b463aea296c3ca05b0.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6ba5f74cd04874b463aea296c3ca05b0.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/6ba5f74cd04874b463aea296c3ca05b0.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大型多人游戏</h2>参与惊心动魄的多人小规模战斗，每艘船最多有 16 名玩家 (*) 乘员，承诺令人振奋的海战。随着雄心勃勃的路线图旨在扩大对抗的规模，Ahoy 准备提供真正无与伦比的海上体验。<br><br><i>(*) 16 名玩家是目前多人游戏的理想目标。并非所有飞船都能支持这种规模的玩家船员，开发中发现的技术探索可能会改变我们每艘船的玩家目标。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/29573d99c05fb0a696a9a9171ac718f5.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/29573d99c05fb0a696a9a9171ac718f5.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/29573d99c05fb0a696a9a9171ac718f5.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有更多...</h2>随着我们不断完善 Ahoy，我们的目标是以一种引人入胜和身临其境的方式概括 18 世纪后期的生活本质。我们邀请您浏览我们网站上的常见问题解答，其中详细介绍了我们当前的目标和对 Ahoy 发展的未来愿望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/18eb4dea6483e31790844a366c54247d.poster.avif?t=1749329345\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/18eb4dea6483e31790844a366c54247d.webm?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787230/extras/18eb4dea6483e31790844a366c54247d.mp4?t=1749329345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >今天的愿望清单！</h2>将 Ahoy 添加到您的愿望清单，关注我们，并加入我们的英语 Discord 社区，这样您就不会错过任何新闻！</h2>",
